			<article class="main container col4">
								<header class="maincol">
										<h1 class="pagetitle">Buying Baja</h1>
										<h2 class="dek singlepagecontainer">On a storied stretch of Mexico’s Baja peninsula, locals fight rich outsiders and rampant development that threaten to transform the coast and dry up aquifers.</h2>
										<section class="singlebyline singlepagecontainer">
						<h3 class="invis">Authored by</h3>
						Story by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/krista-langlois/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Krista Langlois</a>								<br/>
							Photos and video by  
										<a href="https://hakaimagazine.com/profiles/kristina-blanchflower/" class="tagmanager" id="author_link_top" >Kristina Blanchflower</a>								<br/>
												</section>
					 
